Bazel 9 removed cc_library/cc_test from the global builtins; googletest 1.17.0's
root BUILD calls them unloaded. Add the explicit load (rules_cc is made visible
by the RULES_CC_DEP overlay). Upstream-clean on Bazel 8; only needed for Bazel 9.

--- a/BUILD.bazel
+++ b/BUILD.bazel
@@ -1,3 +1,5 @@
+load("@rules_cc//cc:defs.bzl", "cc_binary", "cc_library", "cc_test")
+
